title: Ep. 51 - Power Up
description:
From huddling around fires in the primitive years to congregating around charging stations in airports today, Energy has always been an essential ingredient to our survival...How well are you protecting your energy?
  
 In this Episode:
 1. Burbans and Lacs 2. Shhh...Silence Please 3. Borrowed Charger 4. Karl's New Job 5. Will Vs. Denzel
